#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:1
msgid "E4104"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:3
msgid ""
"Current loop expects different number of arguments than supplied with "
"`continue`."
msgstr "当前循环的参数数量与 `continue` 提供的参数数量不同。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:5
msgid ""
"This error occurs when the number of arguments provided to a `continue` "
"statement does not match the number of arguments expected by the loop. In"
" a `for` loop with explicit loop variables, when using `continue` with "
"arguments, you must provide the same number of arguments as declared in "
"the loop header."
msgstr ""
"此错误发生在 `continue` 语句提供的参数数量与循环所期望的参数数量不匹配时。在带有显式循环变量的 `for` "
"循环中，如果使用带参数的 `continue`，必须提供与循环头中声明的变量数量相同的参数。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:10
msgid ""
"For example, if a `for` loop has two loop variables, any `continue` "
"statement with arguments within that loop must also provide exactly two "
"arguments. Providing too few or too many arguments will trigger this "
"error."
msgstr ""
"例如，如果一个 `for` 循环有两个循环变量，那么该循环中任何带参数的 `continue` 语句也必须正好提供两个参数。参数数量不足或过多都会触发此错误。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:14
msgid ""
"Note that in a `for` loop, you can omit all arguments in a `continue` "
"statement. In this case, the loop will use the update expressions "
"specified in the loop header. However, if you do provide arguments to "
"`continue`, the number of arguments must match the number of loop "
"variables."
msgstr ""
"请注意，在 `for` 循环中，你可以省略 `continue` "
"语句中的所有参数。在这种情况下，循环将使用循环头中指定的更新表达式。但是，如果你为 `continue` "
"提供参数，那么参数数量必须与循环变量数量匹配。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:19
msgid "For example, in a `for` loop with two variables:"
msgstr "例如，在一个有两个变量的 `for` 循环中："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:21
msgid "`continue` (with no arguments) will use the default updates"
msgstr "`continue`（没有参数）将使用默认更新"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:22
msgid "`continue x, y` (with two arguments) is valid"
msgstr "`continue x, y`（有两个参数）是有效的"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:23
msgid "`continue x` or `continue x, y, z` will trigger this error"
msgstr "`continue x` 或 `continue x, y, z` 会触发此错误"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:25
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:27
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn g(x : Int, y : Int) -> Int {\n"
"  for i = x, j = y; i + j < 10; i = i + 1, j = j + 1 {\n"
"    if i < j {\n"
"      continue i + 2, j + 1, i + j\n"
"      //    ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Error: Current loop expects 2 "
"arguments, but\n"
"      //                                       `continue` is supplied "
"with 3 arguments\n"
"    }\n"
"  } nobreak {\n"
"    42\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:31
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:33
msgid ""
"To fix this error, ensure that the number of arguments provided to "
"`continue` matches the number of loop variables. For example,"
msgstr "要修复此错误，请确保 `continue` 提供的参数数量与循环变量数量匹配。例如："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4104.md:36
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn g(x : Int, y : Int) -> Int {\n"
"  for i = x, j = y; i + j < 10; i = i + 1, j = j + 1 {\n"
"    if i < j {\n"
"      continue i + 2, j + 1\n"
"    } else {\n"
"      continue\n"
"    }\n"
"  } nobreak {\n"
"    42\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

